content: While exploring the New West, you will come across a corpse slumped over at a gate. Interact with the corpse to get a mission from the fox. She wants you to take her to the man who took her life. The man in question is Non-Void, and he can be found on the left wing of the New Thunderclap Temple complex.

The content is as follows:
While exploring the New West, you will come across a corpse slumped over at a gate. Interact with the corpse to get a mission from the fox. She wants you to take her to the man who took her life. The man in question is Non-Void, and he can be found on the left wing of the New Thunderclap Temple complex.
